        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "SQA acceptance criteria — MRL 5 Class III device",
        "description": "The CFD solver must operate under a documented quality management system conforming to ISO 9001 or equivalent. Version-controlled source and configuration files, automated regression test suite with >95% pass rate, and a formal change-control log are required. All simulation scripts must be archived with unique version identifiers traceable to the submitted validation report."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 is deployed under an ISO 9001-certified QMS. Automated nightly regression tests covering 312 benchmark cases achieve a 99.4% pass rate. All solver input decks, mesh files, and post-processing scripts are version-controlled in a Git repository with commit hashes recorded in the validation report appendix. Change-control records confirm no solver patches were applied between the verification runs and the COU2 production simulations."
    },
